  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>またこうやってみんなと旅が出来るなんて
思ってもなかったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I never thought we'd be able to journey together like this anymore.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>同じ目的に向かった者同士が、再び別の目的に
向かって集まり、力を合わせるというのがいいな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Travelling together for the same reason yet being called for a different reason than our previous travel. It's good we're able to join forces once again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47044</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;、おっさんくさーい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Klarth&gt; try to hold the grandpa talk in.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おっさんくさいだと？
私はまだ２９だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who's a grandpa!? I'm just 29!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>久しぶりに会ったのですから、
ケンカはやめた方がいいかと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm overjoyed we are all together but please don't fight...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>相変わらずだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seems everyone's the same.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;さんは
どうしたのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;, what is on your mind?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;さんと久しぶりに会うので
照れているのでは……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's been looking forward to meeting with &lt;Arche&gt; for so long, maybe he's shy?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>チェ・ス・ター∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>CHE-S-TER~!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>や、やめろ、なんだよ、
おまえ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cut it out, you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいじゃん、いいじゃん、
久しぶりなんだし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh it's ok! You've been missing me, haven't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_078_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、なんだよ、おまえ、２００年経って
なんか性格変わってねーか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-what's up with you? 200 years passed by and you've not changed one bit!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
